<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/united-kingdom-reserve-forces-association> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The United Kingdom Reserve Forces Association (UKRFA) promotes the efficiency of the reserve forces by providing opportunities for education, personal development and international experiences. UKRFA is part of the Ministry of Defence ."@en .
